    <string name="firstrun_title">Get started</string>
    <string name="firstrun_body">Enter your SyncClipboard server address (host:port). On a LAN the server uses plain HTTP, so traffic isn\'t encrypted. Pull writes the server\'s clipboard to this device; push needs the accessibility permission below.</string>

    <string name="push_needs_accessibility">Push is on, but clipboard capture isn\'t granted. Copies won\'t be pushed until you enable the accessibility service below.</string>

    <string name="notif_rationale">Allow notifications so the sync service can show its ongoing status and keep running in the background.</string>
    <string name="notif_denied">Notifications are off. Background sync may be less reliable without the ongoing notification.</string>

